snippet.title: Alter Army - Forest Boss (WIP)
snippet.description:
This is a WIP first boss fight in Alter Army.

Alter Army is a action platformer game currently in development by 15yr old game developers called Vague Pixels.

You can now add Alter Army to your steam wishlist so go check it out! : http://store.steampowered.com/app/602300/Alter_Army/

You can download the beta of our game from Game Jolt or Itch(the links are below).

Game Jolt :- https://gamejolt.com/games/alterarmy/293815
Itch :- https://vague-pixels.itch.io/-alter-army 

https://www.facebook.com/alterarmy/
https://twitter.com/alterarmy
